    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers practical transportation for a budget-conscious buyer. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the cabin is functional but exhibits clear signs of use, including some wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, though it would benefit from a routine tune-up soon. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable work vehicle or a first car.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
