      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no scratches or dents, while the interior is pristine with no signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained with a full service history. This is a collector-quality example that will satisfy even the most demanding buyer.",
