      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. It shows visible wear on both the interior and exterior surfaces. While all components are currently functional, some mechanical parts may require maintenance or repair in the near future to ensure continued operation.",
      "price": 23500.0,
